<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1437,153,395]" pageId="6" pageNumber="287">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,297,323]" pageId="6" pageNumber="287">Remarks.</emphasis>
The genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Rafinesque" authorityYear="1810" box="[442,542,298,323]" class="Chondrichthyes" family="Rajidae" genus="Dipturus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rajiformes" pageId="6" pageNumber="287" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[442,542,298,323]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="287">Dipturus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is currently under revision and the species from the GOM are of particular interest as little is known of their biology and habits.
